Gabrielle BULMER and Thomas Bulmer, Plaintiffs-Appellants,
v.
UNITYPOINT HEALTH, a/k/a UnityPoint Health-Des Moines, a/k/a Iowa Health System, a/k/a Central Iowa Health System, a/k/a Central Iowa Hospital Corporation, UPH Iowa Lutheran Hospital; Des Moines Orthopaedic Surgeons, P.C.; Wesley Smidt ; and unidentified John Does, Defendants-Appellees. No. 17-2084 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 15, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Plaintiffs in a medical malpractice action appeal the grant of summary judgment for the defendant providers. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
